<! [CDATA[
 Dairyland Canada Logo
Dairyland is a dairy business that operates in Port Coquitlam, British Columbia. Now owned by Saputo Dairy Foods Canada, Dairyland was originally an operating arm of BC dairy farmers' cooperatives and was legally named Agrifoods International Cooperative Ltd. at the time of the sale of the majority of its assets to Saputo Incorporated. Its products are sold across Canada. Dairyworld Foods, a Canadian-based dairy cooperative, was purchased by Saputo Inc.
You can download theDairylandlogo on full-version of the page.
